all_results.question:
In the diagram, $PQRS$ is a trapezoid with an area of $12.$ $RS$ is twice the length of $PQ.$ What is the area of $\triangle PQS?$

[asy]
draw((0,0)--(1,4)--(7,4)--(12,0)--cycle);
draw((7,4)--(0,0));
label("$S$",(0,0),W);
label("$P$",(1,4),NW);
label("$Q$",(7,4),NE);
label("$R$",(12,0),E);
[/asy]

